  "status": "active",
  "reference_number": "RUS2060",
  "remarks": "\nEvgenii Yuryevich AGUREEV is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the following grounds: (1) Evgenii Yuryevich AGUREEV has been and is involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by working as a director or equivalent, of PJSC Alrosa, a Government of Russia-affiliated entity; (2) Evgenii Yuryevich AGUREEV has been and is involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by working as a director or equivalent, of PJSC Alrosa, a business in the Russian extractives sector, a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia.\n",
